message: [[WP:AES|←]]Created page with 'Hi, I'm FútboldeChile and I've come to contribute my knowledge to Wikipedia, mostly in the areas of [[football]] and [[women's soccer]], especially if they are related to my country. I will also be contributing to articles on [[videogame]]s, [[music]] and others of interest to me, either with references, extensions or correcting simple spelling errors. You can leave me a message, a congratulations, a suggestion or whatever you like in my Talk Page:Fútbo...'
